| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4939 — Recovery Inhibition (stormous)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b1bf1976-2163-55de-a496-9a34a7b36a85"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
